summary: The client expressed issues with prior sprint data and proposed wiping it out to start fresh with Sprint 1, inquiring if the SPRINT_PLANNING_ARCHITECT could delete current sprint plans. The SPRINT_PLANNING_ARCHITECT responded by confirming successful updates to stories US-001, US-010, and US-015.

actions.task: Wipe out prior sprint data and start over with Sprint 1 if SPRINT_PLANNING_ARCHITECT cannot delete current plans

risks.risk: Problems with prior sprint data leading to inaccuracies
risks.mitigation: Wipe out prior data and restart with Sprint 1
